  "body": "- [ ] I've [opened a support ticket](https://trufflesuite.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nThe new version of MetaMask produces the following warning message:\r\n\r\nMetaMask: **'ethereum.send(...)' is deprecated and may be removed in the future. Please use 'ethereum.sendAsync(...)' or 'ethereum.request(...)' instead.**\r\nFor more information, see: https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1193\r\nsend\t@\tinpage.js:1\r\n**(anonymous)\t@\ttruffle-contract.min-v4.3.36.js:1**\r\nZoneAwarePromise\t@\tzone-evergreen.js:1387\r\n**get\t@\ttruffle-contract.min-v4.3.36.js:1\r\nstart\t@\ttruffle-contract.min-v4.3.36.js:1**\r\ninvoke\t@\tzone-evergreen.js:372\r\nrun\t@\tzone-evergreen.js:134\r\n(anonymous)\t@\tzone-evergreen.js:1276\r\ninvokeTask\t@\tzone-evergreen.js:406\r\nrunTask\t@\tzone-evergreen.js:178\r\ndrainMicroTaskQueue\t@\tzone-evergreen.js:582\r\nPromise.then (async)\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nThe warning appears when the user denies the operation using the MetaMask Reject button.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* TruffleContract version: 4.3.36\r\n* Web3 version: 1.5.3\r\n\r\n",
